     9       19/2          9        1/2          ✓
    10       21/2         10        1/2          ✓

  All 11 levels: integer = n, remainder = 1/2 (EXACT)

  With physical units (Fraction arithmetic throughout):

    ℏ = 1054571817/10000000000000000000000000000000000000000000 J·s
    ω = 100 rad/s
